  "title": "Solving the Scalability Trilemma",
  "html": "<section class=\"slide\" style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; min-height: 100vh; box-sizing: border-box; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; align-items: center; background-color: var(--bg); color: var(--text); font-family: var(--font-body); padding: 2rem; position: relative; overflow: hidden;\">\n  <style>\n    .slide-grid {\n      display: grid;\n      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;\n      gap: 2rem;\n      width: 100%;\n      max-width: 1200px;\n      margin-top: 2rem;\n    }\n    .slide-title {\n      font-family: var(--font-head);\n      font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.5rem);\n      color: var(--text);\n      text-align: center;\n      margin-bottom: 1rem;\n    }\n    .comparison-card {\n      background: var(--surface);\n      border: 1px solid var(--border);\n      border-radius: 1rem;\n      padding: 1.5rem;\n      box-shadow: 0 0 20px var(--accent-glow);\n      transition: transform 0.3s ease;\n    }\n    .card-header {\n      font-family: var(--font-head);\n      font-size: clamp(1.2rem, 2vw, 1.8rem);\n      color: var(--accent);\n      margin-bottom: 1rem;\n      border-bottom: 2px solid var(--border);\n      padding-bottom: 0.5rem;\n      display: flex;\n      justify-content: space-between;\n      align-items: center;\n    }\n    .point-list {\n      list-style: none;\n      padding: 0;\n      margin: 0;\n    }\n    .point-item {\n      margin-bottom: 1rem;\n      font-size: clamp(0.9rem, 1.5vw, 1.2rem);\n      line-height: 1.5;\n      color: var(--text-muted);\n      display: flex;\n      align-items: flex-start;\n      gap: 0.5rem;\n    }\n    .point-item strong {\n      color: var(--text);\n      display: block;\n    }\n    .trilemma-footer {\n      margin-top: 3rem;\n      text-align: center;\n      padding: 1rem;\n      background: var(--code-bg);\n      border-radius: 0.5rem;\n      font-size: clamp(0.8rem, 1.2vw, 1rem);\n      color: var(--text-muted);\n      border: 1px dashed var(--border);\n      max-width: 800px;\n      margin-left: auto;\n      margin-right: auto;\n    }\n    .reveal {\n      opacity: 0;\n      transform: translateY(20px);\n      animation: revealIn 0.6s forwards;\n      animation-delay: var(--delay);\n    }\n    @keyframes revealIn {\n      to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }\n    }\n    .badge {\n      font-size: 0.7rem;\n      padding: 0.2rem 0.5rem;\n      border-radius: 4px;\n      background: var(--accent);\n      color: var(--bg);\n      text-transform: uppercase;\n      font-weight: bold;\n    }\n  </style>\n\n  <h1 class=\"slide-title reveal visible\" style=\"--delay: 0s\">Solving the Scalability Trilemma</h1>\n\n  <div class=\"slide-grid\">\n    <!-- Left Column: Modular & Layered -->\n    <div class=\"comparison-card reveal visible\" style=\"--delay: 0.2s\">\n      <div class=\"card-header\">\n        <span>Modular Approach</span>\n        <span class=\"badge\">Decentralized</span>\n      </div>\n      <ul class=\"point-list\">\n        <li class=\"point-item\">\n          <div>\n            <strong>Ethereum &amp; Layer 2s</strong>\n            Offloads execution to Rollups (Optimism, Arbitrum) while retaining L1 security.\n          </div>\n        </li>\n        <li class=\"point-item\">\n          <div>\n            <strong>Polkadot Parachains</strong>\n            Native interoperability via a Relay Chain, allowing specialized shards to scale independently.\n          </div>\n        </li>\n        <li class=\"point-item\">\n          <div>\n            <strong>The Trade-off</strong>\n            Prioritizes <em>Security &amp; Decentralization</em>; accepts slight complexity in user experience (bridging).\n          </div>\n        </li>\n      </ul>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- Right Column: Monolithic & Integrated -->\n    <div class=\"comparison-card reveal visible\" style=\"--delay: 0.4s\">\n      <div class=\"card-header\">\n        <span>Monolithic Approach</span>\n        <span class=\"badge\">High Speed</span>\n      </div>\n      <ul class=\"point-list\">\n        <li class=\"point-item\">\n          <div>\n            <strong>Solana's Architecture</strong>\n            Single-state machine with Proof-of-History for massive throughput and sub-second finality.\n          </div>\n        </li>\n        <li class=\"point-item\">\n          <div>\n            <strong>Layer 1 Scaling</strong>\n            Vertical scaling through high-spec hardware and optimized parallel execution (Sealevel).\n          </div>\n        </li>\n        <li class=\"point-item\">\n          <div>\n            <strong>The Trade-off</strong>\n            Prioritizes <em>Speed &amp; Performance</em>; faces challenges in hardware accessibility for validators.\n          </div>\n        </li>\n      </ul>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"trilemma-footer reveal visible\" style=\"--delay: 0.6s\">\n    <strong>The Trilemma:</strong> Security ⬌ Speed ⬌ Decentralization. <br>\n    No single architecture solves all three perfectly; solutions are selected based on the specific use-case requirements.\n  </div>\n</section>",
